trans-unit.source: Represents the root of the .rules files and contains all the <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> and <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition" />s associated with a workflow.
trans-unit.target: Représente la racine des fichiers .rules et contient toutes les classes <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> et <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition" /> associées à un workflow.
Cette classe ne peut pas être héritée.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of rule conditions in the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Obtient la collection de conditions de règle du workflow.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleConditionCollection" /> that contains all the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition" />s in the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleConditionCollection" /> qui contient toutes les classes <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition" /> du workflow.

trans-unit.source: Determines the difference between <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.Conditions" /> and the <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> in the original definition and the changed definition.
trans-unit.target: Détermine la différence entre <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.Conditions" /> et <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> dans la définition d'origine et la définition modifiée.

trans-unit.source: A list of <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.WorkflowChangeAction" /> classes that differentiate the <paramref name="originalDefinition" /> from the <paramref name="changedDefinition" />.
trans-unit.target: Liste de classes <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.WorkflowChangeAction" /> qui distinguent la <paramref name="originalDefinition" /> de la <paramref name="changedDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: Represents the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> that targets the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions" /> property.
Gets the collection of <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> in the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Obtient la collection de <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> du workflow.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSetCollection" /> that contains all the <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> in the workflow.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSetCollection" /> qui contient toutes les <see cref="P:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleDefinitions.RuleSets" /> du workflow.
